title: GO Contact EX Blue Smoke Theme
creator: Themes Architect

extendedInfo.description: App to Go Contacts with the motif of a smoke on a blue background. Subtle background in blue with white smoke is for those who like simple and classic look. The contact name is in white, the date and time in blue, buttons and keys are in the same color as smoke (milky white), numbers are blue and letters are white. The button for dialing has white elements on the smoke background. Other elements are in white. Each tab in contacts looks the same as the main menu of contacts. If you like blue color and smoke motif reminds you campfire with friends or smoking marijuana this theme is perfect for you. Subtle colors cause the contacts list more clear. If you like the color blue with a pattern of smoke and you want it more please see our other projects with this theme. App to Go Contacts with the motif of a smoke on a blue background is free.Requirements:This theme requires GO Contacts EX application installed on your phone. You can download it for free from Google Play typing GO Contacts EX  in search field.This theme contains:- fully customized dialpad and dialbutton. - changed fonts, now they have smoke style- background with cool smokeHow to set our theme as default:1.
